  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Rico, a 9-year-old girl who likes dolls, no longer plays with dolls with the advent of a virtual world called \"Unreal Planet.\" Feeling disappointed, the animal dolls decide to enter the \"Unreal Planet\" to talk to Rico. For some reason, the virtual world doesn't welcome anyone other than children... Will the dolls be able to meet Rico?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/481e41ff405d0d8e714c61fea8429a4a.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/481e41ff405d0d8e714c61fea8429a4a.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/481e41ff405d0d8e714c61fea8429a4a.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solving puzzles using superpowers</h2>The four dolls enter the world of Unreal Planet and gain different superpowers (gravity/time/magnetic/electricity).<br>Use your dolls' superpowers to solve various puzzles and take on the adventure!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/c4b3350c08d6709df5cfd4fe634673ad.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/c4b3350c08d6709df5cfd4fe634673ad.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/c4b3350c08d6709df5cfd4fe634673ad.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/338d42569de4fd27bd758a38391c0913.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/338d42569de4fd27bd758a38391c0913.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/338d42569de4fd27bd758a38391c0913.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/81fe2a78c0aa1d0090230b53a9d82103.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/81fe2a78c0aa1d0090230b53a9d82103.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/81fe2a78c0aa1d0090230b53a9d82103.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/b599c786c5656e6dc5836ce93aa52cfe.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/b599c786c5656e6dc5836ce93aa52cfe.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/b599c786c5656e6dc5836ce93aa52cfe.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with a friend</h2>Both two-player cooperative mode and single play are available.<br>Two people control one doll each, or one person manipulates two dolls!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/ec40f847cdc567264382e8d44775a221.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/ec40f847cdc567264382e8d44775a221.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/ec40f847cdc567264382e8d44775a221.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collaborative skills to move together</h2>In the real world, dolls are easily tangled dolls.<br>Using this concept, we gave the dolls a common ability to be sticked.<br>Stick with other players and solve puzzles!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/477e14b1d9abc4eebb2901ce6eb80ea5.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/477e14b1d9abc4eebb2901ce6eb80ea5.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/477e14b1d9abc4eebb2901ce6eb80ea5.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ride-on adventure</h2>Explore the various attractions of amusement parks in the game Unreal Planet!<br>Each attraction has a different concept.<br>I heard there's even a boss stage?!",
  "about_the_game": "Rico, a 9-year-old girl who likes dolls, no longer plays with dolls with the advent of a virtual world called \"Unreal Planet.\" Feeling disappointed, the animal dolls decide to enter the \"Unreal Planet\" to talk to Rico. For some reason, the virtual world doesn't welcome anyone other than children... Will the dolls be able to meet Rico?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/481e41ff405d0d8e714c61fea8429a4a.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/481e41ff405d0d8e714c61fea8429a4a.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/481e41ff405d0d8e714c61fea8429a4a.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solving puzzles using superpowers</h2>The four dolls enter the world of Unreal Planet and gain different superpowers (gravity/time/magnetic/electricity).<br>Use your dolls' superpowers to solve various puzzles and take on the adventure!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/c4b3350c08d6709df5cfd4fe634673ad.poster.avif?t=1712227533\" width=150 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/c4b3350c08d6709df5cfd4fe634673ad.webm?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2461110/extras/c4b3350c08d6709df5cfd4fe634673ad.mp4?t=1712227533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor